{% extends "base.html.twig" %}

{% block title %}Cards{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
    <h1 style="margin-top:1em">Cards!</h1>
    <div class="two-col-layout">
        <article class=article>
            <p>My first class is "Card" where the card is made,
            and the methods are "setValue", "getValue" and "getAsString". 
            I have a class that inheritance card, "CardGraphic", with the method "getAsString"
            that renders a graphic presentation. I also have two compositions-classes,
            "DeckOfCards" that renders a whole deck, and "Hand" that 
            gives a hand of cards and also takes away the cards from a deck.</p>

            <p>UML-diagram for my classes</p>
            <figure class="center" >
                <img src="{{ asset('img/uml.png') }}" width=400px alt="uml">
            </figure>
        </article>

        <aside class="aside">
            <ul>
                <li><a href="{{path ('card_deck') }}">Show deck</a></li>
                <li><a href="{{path ('card_deck_shuffle') }}">Shuffle deck</a></li>
                <li><a href="{{path ('card_deck_draw') }}">Draw one card</a></li>
                <li><a href="{{path ('card_draw_hand', {num: 5}) }}">Draw 5 cards</a></li>
            </ul> 
        </aside>
    </div>
{% endblock %}